data.description: Welcome to an exclusive haven of luxury living at "The Trails of Rancho Bernardo." This extraordinary custom home, sprawled over an expansive acre, offers a view that simply defies belief. Prepare to be captivated by the breathtaking vistas of the picturesque Lake Hodges Basin from the moment you step inside. Upon entering the open concept great room, prepare to be awestruck by the soaring 12' ceilings and the magnificent 10' custom windows that open up to seamlessly merge the indoor and outdoor spaces, allowing you to connect with nature like never before. Picture yourself cozying up in front of the elegant custom fireplace, surrounded by a sense of tranquility and natural beauty. Entertaining guests will be an absolute delight in the thoughtfully designed kitchen, complete with a generous Quartz Island that serves as the perfect centerpiece for gatherings. And for those who value privacy and convenience, the primary suite is discreetly nestled on the main floor, boasting a custom-designed shower and exquisite countertops. Owned Solar and 2 Owned Tesla batteries in the garage. The home will operate off the grid in a total power outage. Plenty of solar panels and plenty of battery power. Approximately $300 per month. This impeccable residence also offers two spacious rooms, along with a charming "Jack and Jill" bedroom, ensuring ample space for everyone in the family. Venture downstairs to discover an expansive bedroom and living area, leading you to an inviting oasis outside with a bespoke swimming pool accompanied by a cascading waterfall spa, promising endless relaxation and enjoyment. Not only does this home exude elegance, but it also boasts custom wood floors throughout, elevating the ambiance to unmatched heights. Convenience is paramount, and the strategically placed laundry room on the main floor ensures effortless living. Car enthusiasts and storage seekers will delight in the 3-car garage, providing ample space to accommodate all your needs. Given the rarity and allure of this property, it's essential to act swiftly as this incredible opportunity will not be available for long. Prepare to embrace the lifestyle you've always dreamed of at "The Trails of Rancho Bernardo," where luxury, nature, and sophisticated living come together in perfect harmony. Your idyllic retreat awaits.
